    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but it doesn't feel temporary. i've been trying to \"work on myself\" for years and i just keep ending up in the same dark place. some things just aren't meant to be fixed, you know? like a machine that's been crushed too many times. at some point, you just realize the damage is permanent.",
